Typescript Component Folding: This plugin groups files which have same name and different extensions. File name groupings: component|service|pipe|guard|directive|actions|effects|reducer|selectors|state|resolver|datasource|model Extensions folded: css|sass|scss|stylus|styl|less|html|haml|pug|ts|js|json|spec\.ts|.\.ts For instance, app.component.ts, app.component.css, app.component.html, app.component..ts will be grouped a virtual folder named app.component.
